5B6C994D.Line21.6E261: I... I know another way. It’s safer. The old prison wing. It was sealed off years ago, after an earthquake.

6E8CB2DA.Line17.BAE4: You’ll see her soon. We need to get through the market.

ABA2C51A.VoiceDir21.6E261: Desperate. Looking for another solution to how they can get out of the city.

F41459DD.Line3.6E261: You… you’re not him… who are you? The chopping, it stopped and I thought… I thought he was coming for me next…
